name: MELLOVVYELLOVV #001 "Sour Peach Candy"
description: Admit it, sometimes the thing that tastes sour makes you addicted, maybe because it gives you comfort, joy, odd, or even rush and adrenaline. Until it's time you want to come back to the "was" feeling or looking for a new flavor that has only one sweet taste in it, because you already had enough with this sour taste that makes you feel "too much" and restless all the time.
